+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${FULLPKGNAME} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Optional dependencies for Tkabber:

* snack (sound notifications)
* tkimg (support for PNG, JPG images)
* ispell (spell checking)
* tkcon (Tk console)
* tktray (iconify Tkabber)
